---
name: weather-structured
description: Structured output with JSON schema
model:
  id: gpt-4o-mini
  provider: openai
  apiType: chat
  connection:
    kind: key
    apiKey: ${env:OPENAI_API_KEY}
  options:
    temperature: 0
outputs:
  - name: city
    kind: string
    description: The city name
    required: true
  - name: temperature
    kind: integer
    description: Temperature in Fahrenheit
    required: true
  - name: conditions
    kind: string
    description: Weather conditions summary
    required: true
inputs:
  - name: city
    kind: string
    default: Seattle
template:
  format:
    kind: jinja2
  parser:
    kind: prompty
---
system:
You are a weather assistant. Return structured weather data.

user:
What's the weather in {{city}}?
